<section id="business-model">
    <h2>Business Model & Financing</h2>

    <h3>About GuldMount’s Financing Model</h3>
    <p>GuldMount supports small-scale and mid-sized gold miners in Uganda through structured credit solutions. We provide working capital, operational financing, and equipment-backed loans to facilitate steady gold production at negotiated prices.</p>

    <h3>How We Support Miners</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>Advance payments to artisanal miners for daily operations.</li>
        <li>Credit secured against equipment (ball mills, wet mills, excavators).</li>
        <li>Fuel, equipment maintenance, and operational expense financing.</li>
        <li>Purchase of ore and residue for processing.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Investor Partnerships</h3>
    <p>Investors partner with us to pre-finance miners in exchange for discounted gold. Our structured repayment plans and asset-backed lending minimize risk while ensuring steady returns.</p>

    <h3>Our Operational Process</h3>
    <ol>
        <li>Purchase ore and residue from miners.</li>
        <li>Provide credit to cover operational costs.</li>
        <li>Secure repayment through gold deliveries.</li>
        <li>Reinvest into expanding miner support and processing capacity.</li>
    </ol>

    <h3>Data-Driven Credit Management</h3>
    <p>We maintain a miner database tracking licenses, equipment, production, and repayment performance to ensure sustainable financing and operational control.</p>

    <h3>Why Partner with GuldMount?</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>Secure gold supply chain through small-scale miners.</li>
        <li>Scalable financing model with minimal operational risks.</li>
        <li>Trusted consultancy within Uganda’s growing gold sector.</li>
    </ul>

</section>

